%% Diagram: Orchestrated saga with compensating transactions on failure
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Cl as Client
    participant Or as Orchestrator
    participant Od as Order
    participant Pa as Payment
    participant In as Inventory

    Cl->>Or: place order

    Or->>Od: create (PENDING)
    Od-->>Or: ok

    Or->>Pa: reserve
    Pa-->>Or: ok

    Or->>In: reserve
    In--xOr: FAIL

    note over Or,In: Compensate in reverse —\nidempotent, semantic.

    Or->>Pa: release hold
    Pa-->>Or: ok
    Or->>Od: cancel
    Od-->>Or: ok

    Or-->>Cl: failed
